# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok aung san suu kyi is against registering her opposition party for myanmar 's upcoming elections because the ruling junta 's restrictions on the vote are `` unjust , '' her lawyer said tuesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (l / lawyer
            :poss (s2 / she))
      :ARG1 (o / oppose-01
            :ARG0 s2
            :ARG1 (r / register-02
                  :ARG0 s2
                  :ARG1 (p / party
                        :ARG0-of o)
                  :poss s2)
            :ARG2 (e / elect-01
                  :location (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Myanmar"))
                  :time (u / upcoming)))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (j / just-02
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG1 (r2 / restrict-01
                        :ARG0 (j2 / junta
                              :ARG0-of (r3 / rule-03))
                        :ARG1 (v / vote-01))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (s / sue-02
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG1 (b / boy
                              :age (t / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 1
                                    :unit (y / year))
                              :ARG0-of (r / rely-01
                                    :ARG1 (v / ventilator)))
                        :ARG2 (p2 / parent)))
            :ARG1 (u / utility
                  :poss (c / city
                        :location (s2 / state
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Texas")))))
      :op2 (s3 / say-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (j / jeopardize-01
                  :ARG0 u
                  :ARG1 (l / life
                        :poss b)
                  :manner (t2 / turn-off-07
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (p3 / power)
                        :destination (h2 / home
                              :poss p2)
                        :ARG1-of (w / wrong-02)))))

                  :mod (l / last))))

                  :value 1)
            :poss c)

                        :ARG1-of (o2 / open-09)))

                        :ARG1 (t / traffic
